net.hudup.core.alg.cf

Annotation Type CFAnnotation


  • @Documented
 @Target(value=TYPE)
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Inherited
public @interface CFAnnotation
    This annotation indicates that the class to which it is applied is a collaborative filtering (CF) recommendation algorithm. Please see net.hudup.core.alg.cf.MemoryBasedCF and net.hudup.core.alg.cf.ModelBasedCF for more details about CF algorithms.
    Version:
    11.0
    Author:
    Loc Nguyen
